review.reviewBody: Really tasty and would say very close to authentic taste. Generous portion and I was super full after that:) Highly recommend the extra bone broth, really tasty!
The taste of fish sauce and beef is nice but they didnt mention that there are peanuts in this dish. I am severely allergic so it was disappointing not being able to half of it.
Really loved the bun rieu! great flavours in the broth
one of my order was pho with grilled pork. but it came plain. just noodles and broth.
39 Duck vermicelli soup. There is no soup base container. There're vermicelli with duck meat, the extra salad I ordered and the bean sprout bag????
